OL,3,CWorkers' rights Bill could lead to
OL,4,Ccost increases and job cuts, retailers
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FUpcoming laws strengthening the rights
OL,8,Fof UK employees could prompt shops to
OL,9,Fhike prices and cut jobs, a retail
OL,10,Ftrade body has claimed.
OL,12,FAbout half of retailers believe the
OL,13,FGovernment's upcoming employment
OL,14,Frights reforms will lead to higher
OL,15,Fprices for customers, according to a
OL,16,Fpoll by the British Retail Consortium
OL,17,F(BRC).
