OL,3,CWorkers' rights Bill could lead to
OL,4,Ccost increases and job cuts, retailers
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FThe survey of human resources
OL,8,Fdirectors across the retail sector
OL,9,Ffound that a similar amount think the
OL,10,FBill will result in job losses.
OL,12,FThe proposed new law includes a right
OL,13,Fto guaranteed hours, cracking down on
OL,14,Fzero hour contracts without the offer
OL,15,Fof work.
OL,17,FIt will also bring in new restrictions
OL,18,Fon "fire-and-rehire" processes when
OL,19,Femployees are let go and then re-
OL,20,Femployed on new contracts with worse
OL,21,Fpay or conditions.
