OL,3,CWorkers' rights Bill could lead to
OL,4,Ccost increases and job cuts, retailers
OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,FAnd it strengthens trade unions and
OL,8,Fgives workers certain "day one"
OL,9,Frights, such as sick pay, paternity
OL,10,Fleave and the right to request
OL,11,Fflexible working.
OL,13,FThe BRC's survey found companies are
OL,14,Fmost worried about the guaranteed
OL,15,Fhours, which they say could make it
OL,16,Fharder to offer people part-time jobs.
