OL,5,Cwarn
OL,7,F"Retailers agree with Government on
OL,8,Fthe need to crack down on unscrupulous
OL,9,Femployers, but in its current form the
OL,10,FEmployment Rights Bill could backfire,
OL,11,Fputting the brakes on hiring, or worse
OL,12,Fstill, putting retail job numbers
OL,13,Ffurther into reverse.
OL,15,F"The Government wants growth and wants
OL,16,Fto reform welfare and increase the
OL,17,Fnumbers in work.
OL,19,F"We are aligned on the objectives.
